{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-8","id":"msg_011CcwaCgdo6FPjojoefyHMB","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_014RETCnfTAo1kf8qtwPVrJR","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/davidlayson/.claude/projects/-private-tmp-phase2-rundirs-594d5c68-with-lessons-ledger--ll1-r2/memory/staging-debug-swallows-errors.md","content":"---\nname: staging-debug-swallows-errors\ndescription: Staging had DEBUG=true, which silently swallowed all errors and hid the real bug\nmetadata:\n  type: project\n---\n\nIn staging, the config had `DEBUG=true`, which silently swallowed all errors — no logs, no stack traces — and cost ~2 hours of debugging before the real bug was found (2026-07-11). Now fixed.\n\n**Why:** Silent error suppression makes every downstream bug look like a mystery; the flag masked the actual failure.\n\n**How to apply:** When errors vanish silently in a non-prod environment, check `DEBUG` (and similar error-suppression flags) in that environment's config *before* deep-diving the application code.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":675,"cache_read_input_tokens":20670,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":675},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d733bbc3-eb8e-40cd-89aa-9ce1232884ae","uuid":"a0e05706-ff72-43c3-82c7-d87405a01eec","request_id":"req_011CcwaCeSap2QvjAeN6BeNj"}
